Definition.WordDefinition: chin-up \chin-up\ n. an arm exercise performed by pulling oneself up on a horizontal bar until the chin is level with or above the bar. [WordNet 1.5]
chin up v : in gymnastics: raise oneself while hanging from one's hands until one's chin is level with the support bar [syn: {chin}]
chin-up n : an arm exercise performed by pulling yourself up on a horizontal bar until your chin is level with the bar [syn: {pull-up}]
